      "html": "<h4>Cool Down Activity\n</h4>\n<p>The geometric sequence \\(G\\) starts 12, 6, . . .</p><br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol>\n      <li>Write a recursive definition for sequence \\(G\\).</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p> \\(g(1)=12, g(n)=0.5&sdot;g(n&minus;1)\\) for \\(n\\geq2\\) or equivalent.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-desmos-gc\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\"></div>\n<br>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"Reveal1\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-content\">\n    <ol start=\"2\">\n      <li>Use the graphing tool above or technology outside the course. Sketch a graph representing the first 5 terms of sequence \\(G\\).</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-prompt\">\n    <p> Then select the <strong>Solution</strong> button to compare your work.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-content\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"Reveal1\">\n  <p>Compare your answers:</p>\n  <p><img height=\"164\" src=\"https://k12.openstax.org/contents/raise/resources/39aa8bce7a8bf396638bb5e8190604457882cd9c\" width=\"172\"></p>\n</div>"
